title: Better than the original.
review: I defiantly loved this movie. Better and more detailed than the original and the Pennywise was more creepier as well.

title: A great movie.
review: This is a good movie and what makes me laugh is that some people have said that it was more funny than scary. I dont think so. I mean really people if a supernatural clown came after you would you run or sit there and laugh like an idiot. Didnt think so.
